213
00:12:56,462 --> 00:12:59,162
[ PAKU ]
DON'T CRY.
IT'S GOING TO BE ALL RIGHT.

214
00:12:59,196 --> 00:13:00,696
WHAT'S GOING ON OUT THERE?

215
00:13:00,729 --> 00:13:03,129
WHY ARE ALL THOSE MONSTERS
POURING OUT OF THE SKY
LIKE THAT?

216
00:13:03,162 --> 00:13:08,296
WE'RE ALL GONNA DIE.
THE MONSTERS ARE GONNA GET IN
HERE AND THEY'RE GONNA EAT US.

217
00:13:08,329 --> 00:13:13,629
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DIE.
MY FRIENDS ARE OUT THERE NOW,
AND THEY'LL PROTECT US.

218
00:13:13,662 --> 00:13:16,996
[ SCREAMING ]

219
00:13:19,762 --> 00:13:22,362
[ SUGURO ]
NAMAH SAMANTA-BUDDHANAM BHAH!

220
00:13:24,962 --> 00:13:26,396
[ KAMIKI ]
COME ON.
[ GASPS ]

221
00:13:27,829 --> 00:13:30,396
HURRY UP, THIS WAY.

222
00:13:33,696 --> 00:13:35,196
IZUMO!
PAKU!

223
00:13:35,229 --> 00:13:37,662
I'M SORRY IT TOOK SO LONG
TO GET TO YOU.

224
00:13:37,696 --> 00:13:40,962
I NEVER HAD ANY DOUBT
YOU'D BE COMING TO RESCUE US,
IZUMO.

225
00:13:40,996 --> 00:13:42,462
WHERE ARE WE?

226
00:13:42,496 --> 00:13:44,929
THE JAPAN BRANCH OF THE KNIGHTS
OF THE TRUE CROSS.

227
00:13:44,962 --> 00:13:46,662
AFTER THE INFESTATION BEGAN,

228
00:13:46,696 --> 00:13:50,396
THE VATICAN HAD US SET UP
AN EVACUATION CENTER HERE.

229
00:13:50,429 --> 00:13:53,396
THESE WALLS WILL PROTECT US
FROM DEMONIC ATTACKS.

230
00:13:55,396 --> 00:13:57,396
HEY, BON,
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

231
00:13:57,429 --> 00:13:59,596
HAVE EITHER OF YOU GUYS
SEEN MORIYAMA?

232
00:13:59,629 --> 00:14:02,496
COME TO THINK OF IT,
I HAVEN'T SEEN HER IN A WHILE.

233
00:14:02,529 --> 00:14:04,829
MAYBE SHE GOT LOST
IN THE EVACUATION.

234
00:14:04,862 --> 00:14:07,962
DID YOU TRY CALLING HER?
NO. SHE DOESN'T HAVE
A CELL PHONE.

235
00:14:07,996 --> 00:14:09,729
OKAY, NOW I'M WORRIED.

236
00:14:10,696 --> 00:14:12,362
[ GRUNTING ]

237
00:14:15,296 --> 00:14:17,629
- [ GROWLS ]
- [ GASPS ]

238
00:14:19,162 --> 00:14:21,029
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

239
00:14:22,629 --> 00:14:24,429
MS. SHURA.

240
00:14:26,596 --> 00:14:29,496
[ AMAIMON ]
THAT WOMAN IS HOLDING UP
QUITE NICELY AGAINST FATHER.

241
00:14:29,529 --> 00:14:32,296
BUT AT THE END OF THE DAY,
SHE'S STILL MORTAL.

242
00:14:32,329 --> 00:14:34,296
SHE CAN ONLY TAKE
SO MUCH PUNISHMENT.

243
00:14:34,329 --> 00:14:35,896
[ GRUNTING ]

244
00:14:39,829 --> 00:14:42,562
[ GRUNTS ]

245
00:14:42,596 --> 00:14:43,529
[ GASPS ]

246
00:14:43,562 --> 00:14:46,329
OKAY, IS THAT ALL YOU'VE GOT?

247
00:14:48,062 --> 00:14:49,729
NO, I GOT THIS
FOR YOU TOO.

248
00:14:56,862 --> 00:14:58,562
WHAT A PAIN IN THE ASS.

249
00:15:07,162 --> 00:15:09,862
TRYING TO GET THE DROP ON ME?

250
00:15:09,896 --> 00:15:12,929
[ SHURA, THINKING ]
DAMN IT. HE'S NOT AS DUMB
AS I THOUGHT. WHATEVER.

251
00:15:12,962 --> 00:15:16,796
I STILL NEED HIM
TO FOLLOW ME...

252
00:15:16,829 --> 00:15:18,962
OR I'M TOTALLY SCREWED!

253
00:15:18,996 --> 00:15:21,529
KIRIGAKURE ULTIMATE TECHNIQUE.

254
00:15:21,562 --> 00:15:23,629
SNAKE FORM,
WHITE SERPENT ATTACK!

255
00:15:23,662 --> 00:15:24,962
[ SNARLING ]

256
00:15:27,729 --> 00:15:29,362
[ PANTING ]

257
00:15:31,829 --> 00:15:33,562
[ SCREAMS, GRUNTS ]

258
00:15:34,929 --> 00:15:37,062
SHURA!
[ SHIEMI ]
STOP IT!

259
00:15:39,329 --> 00:15:41,529
WELL, WELL, LOOKS LIKE
WE HAVE A VISITOR.

260
00:15:45,429 --> 00:15:48,696
- SHIEMI.
- PLEASE STOP, I BEG YOU.

261
00:15:48,729 --> 00:15:51,996
YUKI WOULD NEVER DO
SOMETHING THIS CRUEL.

262
00:15:52,029 --> 00:15:53,829
AND WHO ARE YOU
SUPPOSED TO BE?

263
00:15:53,862 --> 00:15:55,296
ONE OF HIS LITTLE FRIENDS?

264
00:15:55,329 --> 00:15:59,096
YES. HE'S REALLY PRECIOUS TO ME.

265
00:15:59,129 --> 00:16:02,962
SO PLEASE GIVE HIM BACK!

266
00:16:02,996 --> 00:16:05,096
DON'T MAKE ME LAUGH!

267
00:16:05,129 --> 00:16:08,262
NEE!

268
00:16:08,296 --> 00:16:10,362
[ AMAIMON ]
SHE JUST BLOCKED
FATHER'S FLAMES.

269
00:16:10,396 --> 00:16:12,929
THAT'S JAPANESE ROWAN.
IT WON'T CATCH FIRE...

270
00:16:12,962 --> 00:16:16,729
EVEN IF YOU THROW IT
IN A WHITE-HOT OVEN
AND TURN THE HEAT UP TO 11.

271
00:16:16,762 --> 00:16:19,229
GOOD CALL ON HER PART,
DON'T YOU AGREE?

272
00:16:19,262 --> 00:16:20,729
- [ CRACKING ]
- [ GASPS ]

273
00:16:21,929 --> 00:16:24,496
[ GROANING ]

274
00:16:24,529 --> 00:16:25,796
NEE!

275
00:16:25,829 --> 00:16:28,062
YOU'RE LITTLE PET
CAN BLOCK MY FLAMES,

276
00:16:28,096 --> 00:16:30,762
BUT WITHOUT IT
YOU DON'T STAND
MUCH OF A CHANCE, DO YOU?

277
00:16:30,796 --> 00:16:34,229
YU... KI, STOP.

278
00:16:34,262 --> 00:16:36,329
- SHIEMI!
- [ GROWLING ]

279
00:16:39,129 --> 00:16:41,029
[ GROANING ]

280
00:16:41,062 --> 00:16:42,996
[ GRUNTING ]

281
00:16:44,929 --> 00:16:48,429
GOD DAMN IT, LET HER GO!

282
00:16:49,396 --> 00:16:51,796
IDIOT. YOU'RE EARLY.

283
00:16:51,829 --> 00:16:54,396
AHA, SO THERE YOU ARE.

284
00:16:54,429 --> 00:16:57,196
AND WITH EVERYONE ELSE
OUT OF THE WAY,

285
00:16:57,229 --> 00:17:00,329
WHY DON'T WE SETTLE THIS
RIGHT HERE AND NOW.

286
00:17:01,696 --> 00:17:04,762
I'M NOT GONNA FIGHT
MY LITTLE BROTHER.
WHAT?

287
00:17:04,796 --> 00:17:08,029
YUKIO, I KNOW YOU'RE IN THERE.
COME ON, WAKE UP.

288
00:17:08,062 --> 00:17:13,429
[ LAUGHS ]
YOU REALLY THINK YOU'RE GOING
TO SAVE YOUR BROTHER?

289
00:17:13,462 --> 00:17:16,429
- HOW TOUCHING.
- [ GRUNTS ]

290
00:17:16,462 --> 00:17:19,496
WAKE UP, YUKIO.
IT'S ME--

291
00:17:19,529 --> 00:17:23,362
YOU'RE WASTING YOUR TIME.
YOUR BROTHER BELONGS TO ME NOW.

292
00:17:23,396 --> 00:17:27,029
STOP CALLING HIM.
HE CAN'T HEAR YOU ANYMORE.

293
00:17:27,062 --> 00:17:28,596
[ GURGLES ]

294
00:17:28,629 --> 00:17:31,962
I KNOW YOU CAN HEAR ME, YUKIO.

295
00:17:31,996 --> 00:17:34,762
YUKIO!

296
00:17:34,796 --> 00:17:37,896
[ ECHOING ]

297
00:17:48,002 --> 00:17:50,302
YUKIO.

298
00:17:50,335 --> 00:17:52,802
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHEN TO GIVE UP.

299
00:17:52,835 --> 00:17:54,669
[ THINKING ]
YUKIO.

300
00:17:56,735 --> 00:18:00,269
COME ON, OPEN YOUR EYES!

301
00:18:00,302 --> 00:18:03,769
YUKIO!

302
00:18:05,269 --> 00:18:06,402
[ METALLIC CLINKING ]

303
00:18:06,435 --> 00:18:07,935
[ GASPS ]

304
00:18:07,969 --> 00:18:09,669
RIN.

305
00:18:11,202 --> 00:18:13,169
RIN!

306
00:18:13,202 --> 00:18:16,102
[ GRUNTING ]

307
00:18:16,135 --> 00:18:18,802
[ YOUNG YUKIO ]
I WON'T LET YOU GO.

308
00:18:18,835 --> 00:18:21,169
YOU DON'T REALLY THINK
YOU CAN ESCAPE, DO YOU?

309
00:18:21,202 --> 00:18:23,869
YOU KNOW HOW MUCH
YOU REALLY HATE RIN.

310
00:18:23,902 --> 00:18:26,669
RIN NEVER KNEW
WHAT WAS GOING ON AROUND US,

311
00:18:26,702 --> 00:18:31,502
BUT EVER SINCE I CAN REMEMBER,
I'VE ALWAYS SEEN
THE DEMONS IN THE DARK.

312
00:18:31,535 --> 00:18:33,669
IT'S NOT TRUE.
YOU'RE LYING.

313
00:18:33,702 --> 00:18:37,935
AS LONG AS I CAN REMEMBER,
RIN ALWAYS DID
THE THINGS I NEVER COULD.

314
00:18:37,969 --> 00:18:40,635
- [ GASPS ]
- EVEN WITHOUT TRYING,

315
00:18:40,669 --> 00:18:43,135
RIN ALWAYS GETS THE THINGS
I CAN NEVER HAVE.

316
00:18:43,169 --> 00:18:44,635
IT'S SO UNFAIR!

317
00:18:44,669 --> 00:18:47,369
I HATE RIN.
IF ONLY HE WERE DEAD.

318
00:18:47,402 --> 00:18:51,035
- IF ONLY HE WAS NEVER BORN!
- NO, THAT'S NOT TRUE!

319
00:18:51,069 --> 00:18:53,269
I-- I--

320
00:18:58,569 --> 00:19:00,769
RIN.
[ GASPS ]

321
00:19:00,802 --> 00:19:05,102
HELP ME, RIN.

322
00:19:05,135 --> 00:19:07,002
[ GROANING ]

323
00:19:07,035 --> 00:19:09,369
YUKIO!

324
00:19:09,402 --> 00:19:12,002
[ ALL SHOUTING ]
RIN! RIN!

325
00:19:14,135 --> 00:19:16,035
RIN! RIN!

326
00:19:17,602 --> 00:19:20,402
[ GASPING ]

327
00:19:24,169 --> 00:19:26,302
[ GRUNTING ]

328
00:19:26,335 --> 00:19:28,202
[ SHOUTS ]

329
00:19:32,002 --> 00:19:33,202
[ GUNSHOT ]

330
00:19:45,869 --> 00:19:49,169
- [ SHURA ]
RIN!
- [ GASPING ]

331
00:19:50,302 --> 00:19:52,169
[ YUKIO WEEPING ]

332
00:19:52,202 --> 00:19:54,435
[ SCREAMING ]

333
00:19:59,402 --> 00:20:01,869
[ SATAN ]
I NEVER THOUGHT
YOU'D REGAIN YOUR SENSES.

334
00:20:01,902 --> 00:20:04,769
BUT I'M NOT LETTING YOU
GET AWAY.
YOU BELONG TO ME.

335
00:20:04,802 --> 00:20:07,135
GO AHEAD, FINISH HIM OFF.
KILL HIM.

336
00:20:07,169 --> 00:20:11,302
WITHOUT HIM AROUND,
WE CAN FINALLY CREATE
THE WORLD WE'VE DREAMED OF.

337
00:20:11,335 --> 00:20:12,502
[ CRYING ]

338
00:20:12,535 --> 00:20:14,969
DO IT!

339
00:20:15,002 --> 00:20:17,135
<i>- DO IT!</i>
- [ CRYING CONTINUES ]

340
00:20:17,169 --> 00:20:18,869
NOW!

341
00:20:20,135 --> 00:20:21,669
I WON'T!

342
00:20:21,702 --> 00:20:24,335
<i>- WHAT DID YOU SAY?</i>
- YOU'RE GONNA DIE.

343
00:20:24,369 --> 00:20:26,135
I'M GOING TO KILL US BOTH!

344
00:20:26,169 --> 00:20:27,935
YOU BASTARD!

345
00:20:27,969 --> 00:20:29,902
YUKI... O.

346
00:20:29,935 --> 00:20:32,035
GODDAMN RETCHED PRIEST!

347
00:20:32,069 --> 00:20:36,169
DO YOU THINK YOU CAN KILL ME
BY COMMITTING SUICIDE?
RIDICULOUS!

348
00:20:36,202 --> 00:20:40,202
I PROMISED MY FATHER
I'D PROTECT MY BROTHER!

349
00:20:40,235 --> 00:20:43,335
IF SUICIDE'S THE ONLY WAY
TO SAVE HIM AND EVERYONE ELSE,

350
00:20:43,369 --> 00:20:45,002
THEN I WILL KILL MYSELF!

351
00:20:45,035 --> 00:20:47,102
[ SATAN ]
STOP! DON'T DO IT!

352
00:20:47,135 --> 00:20:50,135
IF YOU DIE, THE WORLD
YURI AND I DREAMED OF
WILL DIE WITH YOU!

353
00:20:50,169 --> 00:20:52,769
[ SHOUTING ]

354
00:21:00,035 --> 00:21:01,502
SHUT UP.

355
00:21:01,535 --> 00:21:04,335
LET SOMEONE ELSE
BE THE HERO FOR ONCE.

356
00:21:04,369 --> 00:21:08,235
YOU THINK KILLING SATAN
BY OFFING YOURSELF'S
THE BEST YOU CAN COME UP WITH?

357
00:21:08,269 --> 00:21:10,302
- BULLSHIT!
- [ GASPS ]

358
00:21:10,335 --> 00:21:12,902
YOU KNOW WHAT IT FEELS LIKE.

359
00:21:12,935 --> 00:21:15,702
WHEN DAD DIED,
BOTH OF US WERE LEFT BEHIND.

360
00:21:17,335 --> 00:21:19,935
AND I JUST--

361
00:21:19,969 --> 00:21:24,335
I NEVER EVER WANNA FEEL
THAT WAY AGAIN.

362
00:21:24,369 --> 00:21:26,935
[ SOBS ]
I KNOW, RIN.

363
00:21:28,169 --> 00:21:31,035
[ HISSING ]

364
00:21:35,035 --> 00:21:38,135
[ SOBBING ]
I'M SORRY, RIN.

365
00:21:38,169 --> 00:21:40,802
I'M SORRY.

366
00:21:46,735 --> 00:21:49,302
[ RUMBLING ]
CRAP. NOW WHAT?

367
00:21:49,335 --> 00:21:53,069
[ SATAN LAUGHING ]

368
00:21:53,102 --> 00:21:56,335
WHAT'S GOING ON?
THAT'S SATAN.

369
00:21:56,369 --> 00:21:58,002
WHAT A SURPRISE.

370
00:21:58,035 --> 00:22:01,269
I NEVER DREAMED
I COULD BE KNOCKED OFF
MY FEET LIKE THAT.

371
00:22:01,302 --> 00:22:05,669
UNFORTUNATELY FOR YOU,
MY DREAM IS NOT QUITE OVER!

372
00:22:09,102 --> 00:22:11,169
[ SHRIEKING ]

373
00:22:11,202 --> 00:22:15,002
- WHAT THE HELL?
- IT'S THE GEHENNA GATE.

374
00:22:15,035 --> 00:22:17,235
[ CHUCKLING ]

375
00:22:17,269 --> 00:22:20,202
[ MEPHISTO ]
THE WAR BETWEEN THE DEMONS
AND HUMANKIND...

376
00:22:20,235 --> 00:22:22,102
IS APPROACHING ITS CLIMAX!

377
00:22:22,135 --> 00:22:25,069
PREPARE YOURSELVES,
MY YOUNG BROTHERS.

378
00:22:25,102 --> 00:22:29,402
LET'S SEE HOW YOU FARE IN BATTLE
AGAINST OUR RAMPAGING FATHER.

379
00:22:39,635 --> 00:22:42,269
♪ [ WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

380
00:24:02,669 --> 00:24:04,002
[ YUKIO ]
HAVE YOU EVER THOUGHT...

381
00:24:04,035 --> 00:24:06,702
MAYBE IT WASN'T RIGHT
THAT YOU AND I WERE BORN?

382
00:24:06,735 --> 00:24:08,769
[ RIN GRUNTS ]
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT LIGHT?

383
00:24:08,802 --> 00:24:11,335
[ MEPHISTO ]
THE CONTRACT IS SEALED.

384
00:24:11,369 --> 00:24:13,802
NOW THEN,
I BID YOU ADIEU.

